---
import BlogPost from '@/layouts/BlogPost.astro';

const title = "Airbnb ROI Calculator Malaysia: Calculate Your Real Profit 2026";
const description = "Use our interactive Airbnb ROI calculator for Melaka. Compare self-management vs. iHousing's flat-fee model. Get real projections based on 700+ properties.";
const image = "/images/blog/airbnb-investment-calculator.jpg";
const date = "2026-03-04";
const category = "solution-aware-roi";
const language = "en";

const content = `
<div class="calculator-container bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-green-100 my-8">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-green-800">Interactive Airbnb ROI Calculator</h2>
  
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
    <!-- Inputs -->
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Property Purchase Price (RM)</label>
        <input type="number" id="purchasePrice" value="350000" class="w-full p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-500 outline-none" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Furnishing & Setup (RM)</label>
        <input type="number" id="furnishingCost" value="30000" class="w-full p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-500 outline-none" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Average Nightly Rate (RM)</label>
        <input type="number" id="nightlyRate" value="180" class="w-full p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-500 outline-none" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Expected Occupancy (%)</label>
        <input type="range" id="occupancy" min="40" max="95" value="70" class="w-full h-2 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg appearance-none cursor-pointer accent-green-600" />
        <div class="text-right text-sm text-gray-600 font-medium"><span id="occupancyVal">70</span>%</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Results Card -->
    <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-green-200 flex flex-col justify-center">
      <div class="mb-4">
        <div class="text-sm text-green-700 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Estimated Annual Net Profit</div>
        <div class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-green-900">RM <span id="annualProfit">0</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-6">
        <div class="text-sm text-green-700 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Cash-on-Cash ROI</div>
        <div class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-green-900"><span id="roiPercentage">0</span>%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-xs text-green-600 italic">
        *Calculated based on iHousing's RM250/mo flat fee model + estimated platform fees/utilities.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script is:inline>
  function calculateROI() {
    const purchasePrice = parseFloat(document.getElementById('purchasePrice').value) || 0;
    const furnishing = parseFloat(document.getElementById('furnishingCost').value) || 0;
    const rate = parseFloat(document.getElementById('nightlyRate').value) || 0;
    const occupancy = parseFloat(document.getElementById('occupancy').value) / 100;
    
    document.getElementById('occupancyVal').innerText = Math.round(occupancy * 100);

    const totalInvestment = purchasePrice + furnishing;
    const monthlyRevenue = rate * 30 * occupancy;
    
    // Expenses
    const platformFees = monthlyRevenue * 0.10; // 10% average
    const utilitiesInternet = 250;
    const maintenance = 150;
    const managementFee = 250; // iHousing Flat Fee
    
    const monthlyExpenses = platformFees + utilitiesInternet + maintenance + managementFee;
    const monthlyNet = monthlyRevenue - monthlyExpenses;
    const annualNet = monthlyNet * 12;
    const roi = (annualNet / totalInvestment) * 100;

    document.getElementById('annualProfit').innerText = Math.max(0, Math.round(annualNet)).toLocaleString();
    document.getElementById('roiPercentage').innerText = Math.max(0, roi.toFixed(1));
  }

  // Listen to all inputs
  ['purchasePrice', 'furnishingCost', 'nightlyRate', 'occupancy'].forEach(id => {
    document.getElementById(id).addEventListener('input', calculateROI);
  });

  // Initial calculation
  calculateROI();
</script>

<p>Before investing RM350,000+ in a Melaka property, you need to know the <strong>real Physics of ROI.</strong> Most calculators use hypothetical best-case scenarios. At iHousing, we manage 700+ properties and use real data from the ground.</p>

<h2>The 20% Commission Trap</h2>
<p>In Melaka, most management companies charge 20% of your revenue. If your property earns RM5,000, they take RM1,000. This kills your ROI.</p>

<p><strong>iHousing uses a Flat Fee model (RM200-300).</strong> This ensures that as your revenue grows, your profit grows faster. You keep the upside.</p>

<h3>Example: RM5,000 Monthly Revenue</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Standard 20% Agency:</strong> You pay RM1,000. Your Net: RM4,000.</li>
  <li><strong>iHousing Flat Fee:</strong> You pay RM250. Your Net: RM4,750.</li>
  <li><strong>The iHousing Advantage:</strong> RM750 extra in your pocket <em>every single month</em>.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Realistic ROI Benchmarks in Melaka (2026)</h2>
<table class="w-full mb-8">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Property Type</th>
      <th>Avg ROI (Flat Fee)</th>
      <th>Key Success Factor</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>Beachfront Condo (Klebang)</td>
      <td>9% - 11%</td>
      <td>Weekend family demand</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Heritage Shophouse (Jonker)</td>
      <td>12% - 15%</td>
      <td>Scarcity & Premium Rates</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>City Center Studio (Melaka Raya)</td>
      <td>7% - 9%</td>
      <td>Business & Solo Travelers</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h2>Why Our Projections are Different</h2>
<p>We don't just "guess" occupancy. We link our data directly to the local event calendar, Singapore holiday exodus, and weekend Jonker Walk traffic patterns. Our calculator assumes:</p>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Multi-platform distribution:</strong> Not just Airbnb, but Agoda and Booking.com.</li>
  <li><strong>Dynamic Pricing:</strong> Rates that adjust automatically to demand spikes.</li>
  <li><strong>Professional Housekeeping:</strong> 5-star cleanliness which justifies 15-20% higher rates.</li>
</ol>

<div class="bg-green-900 text-white p-8 rounded-2xl text-center my-12">
  <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Want a Custom Data-Back ROI Projection?</h2>
  <p class="mb-6">Send us your property location and we will pull the last 12 months of actual revenue data from nearby units.</p>
  <a href="https://wa.me/60123456789?text=Hi%20iHousing,%20I'd%20like%20a%20custom%20ROI%20projection%20for%20my%20Melaka%20property" class="bg-white text-green-900 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-green-100 transition-colors inline-block">
    WhatsApp for Free Data Audit
  </a>
</div>
`;

---
<BlogPost
  title={title}
  description={description}
  image={image}
  date={date}
  category={category}
  language={language}
  content={content}
/>
